These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, coach
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, taxi
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the coach is the owner of the cat##1
4. the musician is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage    | iced-tea       | hot-chocolate  |
| Job         | musician | coach |
| Pet         | ferret        | cat     |
| Sport       | snowboarding     | basketball  |
| Transport   | bike    | taxi     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, fisherman
2 different pets are kept: goat, snake
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, rowing
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi
1. the fisherman is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the goat is the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the owner of the goat is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |       2       |
| Beverage    | mirinda  | iced-tea        |
| Job         | fisherman | teacher     |
| Pet         | snake  | goat        |
| Sport       | water-polo  | rowing |
| Transport   | taxi      | snowmobile        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-3::.
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, broccoli
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, analyst
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, gospel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, sailing
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far left##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the lawyer##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |    2     |
| Food          | broccoli             | kiwi  |
| Hobby         | skydiving         | photography  |
| Job           | lawyer | analyst  |
| Music-Genre   | jazz         | gospel      |
| Sport         | sailing      | rugby |

