.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-4::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, onion
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, entrepreneur
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, sports
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, nigerian
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, helicopter
1. the person eating onion is on the far right##1
2. the polish is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Food          | apple    | onion     |
| Job           | photographer   | entrepreneur |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | sports     |
| Nationality   | polish  | nigerian    |
| Transport     | tram | helicopter       |

