The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the fan of metal is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | tea        | sprite       |
| Hobby         | writing  | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | mystery    |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | folk      |
| Sport         | skiing | badminton     |

