.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, collecting
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, disaster
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, d&b
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby         | board-games     | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | blues |
| Pet           | mouse         | hedgehog     |
| Sport         | soccer  | lacrosse |

 